properties.Name: PolicyStatusType
properties.Description:
The current status of the Policy.

Ex:
- In effect
- Application under review
- Terminated
- Lapsed
- Denied Renewal
- Cancelled by Customer
- Cancelled by Company
- Unpaid / Overdue
- Application pending medical review
- Application accepted/Policy to be issued
- Application pending additional documentation
- Application under investigation
- Void  = A policy contract that for some reason specified in the policy becomes free of all legal effect. One example under which a policy could be voided is when information a policyholder provided is proven untrue.

Columns.Name: PolicyStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Policy Status Type.

Columns.Name: PolicyStatusTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Policy Status Type.

Columns.Name: PolicyStatusTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Policy Status Type.
